  <brief_title>Survey Conducted Among Early Breast Cancer Patients Treated With Arimidex for Evaluation of Treatment Adherence</brief_title>
  <acronym>ARIADNE</acronym>
  <official_title>Survey and Follow-up of the Treatment Adherence and Medication Habits of Early Breast Cancer Patients on Adjuvant Hormonal Therapy With the Aromatase Inhibitor Arimidex</official_title>
  <sponsors>
